{
  "description": "This image depicts a vibrant, illuminated fountain in an outdoor plaza. The fountain is tiered, with water shooting upwards in a central spray, all lit with a cool green glow. It's surrounded by a circular, stone-like base that is also illuminated from underneath with warm yellow lighting. The plaza is paved with rectangular stone tiles. In the background, a hillside rises, dotted with trees showing autumnal colors, primarily red and orange. A children's play structure, brightly colored, is visible to the left. A few lampposts punctuate the scene, adding to the overall brightness. A single person is seated near the fountain.",
